[[File:Bundesarchiv B 145 Bild-F077589-0007, Bundesrat, Sitzung.jpg|thumb|[[Johannes Rau]] on 26. February 1988]]
The '''Westdeutsche Allgemeine Zeitung''' is a leading commercial newspaper from [[Essen]], [[Germany]], published by [[WAZ-Mediengruppe]].

It was founded by [[Erich Brost]] and first published 3 April 1948.<ref name=Brost>[http://www.brost.org/erich-brost-1+M52087573ab0.html Biography of Erich Brost]</ref>

